  profileSection = `[사용자 프로필]\n전공: ${major}\n희망진로: ${careerGoal || '미입력'}\n남은학기: ${remainingSemesters || '미입력'}\n\n`;
}

const deptItems = items.filter(i => i.source && i.source.startsWith('학과공지') && i.date);
const schoolItems = items.filter(i => i.source && i.source === '학교공지' && i.date);
const otherItems = items.filter(i => i.source && !i.source.startsWith('학과공지') && i.source !== '학교공지' && i.date);

const noticeList = [
  ...deptItems.slice(0, 12),
  ...otherItems.slice(0, 8),
  ...schoolItems.slice(0, 10)
].map(i => {
  const range = i.dateRange ? i.dateRange : (() => {
    if (!i.date) return '';
    const d = new Date(i.date);
    return `${d.getMonth()+1}/${d.getDate()}`;
  })();
  return `[${i.source}] ${i.title} | ${range} | ${i.url || ''}`;
}).join('\n');

const noticeText = profileSection + noticeList;

return [{ json: { items, total: items.length, noticeText } }];

